WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Do I know your opinion of the Arabic language?

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Of course Reem, I love this kind of dialogue.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:19.000
Well, when did the Arabic language appear?

00:00:19.000 --> 00:00:23.000
The Arabic language has appeared many years ago.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Arabic has been a very long time

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:29.000
and historians pointed out that it is one of the most

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:32.000
prominent languages and it is the most

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:35.000
advanced language in the world.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:38.000
Why is learning Arabic difficult?

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:41.000
It is not like that.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:44.000
Rather, the diversity of Arabic language

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:47.000
