00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:17.000
because it is the only language at the level

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:20.000
of the world that contains the letter DAD.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:23.000
Do you always get high marks in Arabic?

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:26.000
And the teacher describes you as

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:29.000
in love with the Arabic language.

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:32.000
Why?

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:35.000
How can I not love it?

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:38.000
The Creator has honored it and made it

00:01:38.000 --> 00:01:41.000
the language of the Holy Quran and the language

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:44.000
of the Master of Messengers, which is the

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:47.000
language of the President and the cradle

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:50.000
of civilizations around the world.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:53.000
How beautiful is the Arabic language!

